              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-red-900 dark:text-red-200">Emergency service request</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-red-900/90 dark:text-red-200/90 leading-relaxed">
                We will triage this as a priority. Summarize the impact, who is affected, and any deadline in your remarks.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div id="ict-type-blurb-major" class="ict-type-blurb hidden rounded-xl border border-amber-200/80 dark:border-amber-900/50 bg-amber-50/80 dark:bg-amber-950/30 p-4 sm:p-5">
