              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-amber-900/90 dark:text-amber-200/90 leading-relaxed">
                Please outline scope, timeline, and any dependencies. ICTO may follow up to schedule the work.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div id="ict-type-blurb-routine" class="ict-type-blurb hidden rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600 bg-slate-50/90 dark:bg-slate-800/50 p-4 sm:p-5">
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Routine maintenance checklist</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
